WEBVTT

00:14.231 --> 00:15.497
Oh. Hi, Pinkie Pie.

00:15.595 --> 00:18.799
<i>This is your singing telegram
I hope it finds you well</i>

00:18.799 --> 00:21.771
<i>You're invited to a party
Cause we think you're really swell</i>

00:21.771 --> 00:24.677
<i>Gummy's turning one year old
So help us celebrate</i>

00:24.677 --> 00:27.836
<i>The cake will be delicious
The festivities first-rate</i>

00:28.426 --> 00:31.400
<i>There will be games and dancing
Bob for apples, cut a rug</i>

00:31.400 --> 00:34.389
<i>And when the party's over
We'll gather round for a group hug</i>

00:35.101 --> 00:38.842
<i>No need to bring a gift
Being there will be enough</i>

00:39.008 --> 00:42.800
<i>Birthdays mean having fun with friends
Not getting lots of stuff</i>

00:43.332 --> 00:48.171
<i>It won't be the same without you
So we hope that you say yes</i>

00:48.171 --> 00:52.636
<i>So please, oh please, R.S.V.P.
And come and be our guest</i>

00:56.681 --> 01:00.503
Next time I think I'll just
pass out written invitations.

01:48.818 --> 01:51.639
Nice one. Now let me show you
how it's really done.

01:52.290 --> 01:53.119
Hey, girls!

01:53.572 --> 01:54.565
Hey, Pinkie Pie.

01:54.904 --> 01:55.680
Howdy!

01:55.950 --> 01:59.161
Just wanted to tell you how happy I am
that you could make it to Gummy's party.

01:59.295 --> 02:01.746
