missed it for the world.

02:02.143 --> 02:03.104
Me neither.

02:03.104 --> 02:06.149
When Pinkie Pie throws a party, I am there!

02:08.656 --> 02:09.966
TADA!

02:10.198 --> 02:12.038
Ah, it's just a boring old apple.

02:12.038 --> 02:14.528
Don't worry. There're plenty of other surprises in there.

02:14.958 --> 02:16.322
What kind of surprises?

02:16.398 --> 02:19.565
I can't tell you that, silly.
Then it wouldn't be a surprise!

02:34.418 --> 02:36.792
This punch is simply divine.

02:36.792 --> 02:40.304
Is this the same recipe you used
for your "Spring has Sprung" party?

02:40.400 --> 02:41.695
No, something new.

02:46.595 --> 02:48.222
It's Gummy's favorite!

02:53.852 --> 02:56.084
Ooh! This is my jam!

03:00.335 --> 03:01.162
Having fun?

03:01.228 --> 03:02.525
A blast!

03:02.525 --> 03:05.531
You always throw the best parties, Pinkie Pie.

03:05.631 --> 03:08.584
They're always the best parties,
cause my best friends are always there!

03:12.981 --> 03:14.578
Come on, everypony!

03:16.116 --> 03:18.460
Gummy wants to dance!

03:18.761 --> 03:22.399
Go Gummy! It's ya birthday!
Go Gummy! It's ya birthday!

03:27.838 --> 03:30.443
