There's still some cake left.

03:44.433 --> 03:47.019
Uh... I think I'm gonna pass.

03:47.585 --> 03:50.175
Great party, though.
We should do this again soon.

03:53.356 --> 03:55.502
We should do this again soon!

04:06.423 --> 04:07.517
Oh. Hi, Pinkie...

04:07.517 --> 04:08.436
It's soon!

04:08.702 --> 04:09.556
Pardon me?

04:09.648 --> 04:12.276
You said we should have
another party soon and... it's soon!

04:12.615 --> 04:14.176
Here is your invitation!

04:14.927 --> 04:17.772
"You're invited to Gummy's after-birthday party."

04:17.772 --> 04:19.739
"This afternoon at 3 o'clock."

04:19.860 --> 04:21.415
All our bestest friends are invited...

04:21.415 --> 04:24.555
...and here's gonna be dancing and games
and cake and ice cream and punch...

04:24.931 --> 04:26.359
This afternoon?

04:26.629 --> 04:29.216
