05:14.843 --> 05:17.126
That's funny. That's just what Twilight said.

05:17.126 --> 05:19.909
And the answer is "Yes, it's this afternoon".

05:20.029 --> 05:22.427
Oh... Well, I... I, uh...

05:22.427 --> 05:24.265
I don't think I can make it, cause, uh...

05:24.265 --> 05:25.394
I have to, uh...

05:26.020 --> 05:28.141
Uh, you know... I, uh...

05:28.141 --> 05:28.985
Pick apples!

05:29.145 --> 05:31.470
Yep, apples, cause that's what we do.

05:31.470 --> 05:34.123
