06:58.377 --> 07:01.984
Huh. No Twilight, no Applejack, no Rarity.

07:02.687 --> 07:06.161
Oh well. A party is still a party,
even with only two guests.

07:07.387 --> 07:08.722
This afternoon?

07:08.822 --> 07:10.140
-As in...
-Yes!

07:10.271 --> 07:12.263
