08:07.370 --> 08:08.631
-Collect seashells.
-Play volleyball.

08:09.185 --> 08:10.382
-Play volleyball.
-Collect seashells.

08:10.809 --> 08:12.072
-Collect volleyball.
-Play seashells.

08:13.895 --> 08:14.936
