10:22.531 --> 10:25.409
Oh, good. I'd hate for her to ruin everything.

10:25.579 --> 10:26.480
Me too.

10:53.165 --> 10:55.291
-Have you seen her?
-Not since this morning.

10:55.291 --> 11:00.162
